Subject: {{group.name}} collective {{month}} report

{{> header}}

<style>

h1 {
  font-weight:normal;
}

h2 {
  margin-top: 30px;
  color:#75cc1f;
  font-weight:normal;
}

ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

ul li {
  margin: 5px 0px;
}
.counter {
  font-size: 36px;
  color: #7FADF2;
}
.delta {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
.label {

}
.reimbursed {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
</style>

<div style="font-size:10pt">

<h1>{{group.name}} {{month}} report</h1>

<p>Hi there! This your new monthly report for your open collective. In this report, you will find your latest balance (as of the last day of last month) and all the expenses that were submitted.
We hope it's useful. Don't hesitate to send us your feedback by replying to this email. You can always visit your collective page to get the latest up to date data: <a href="{{group.publicUrl}}">{{group.publicUrl}}</a></p>

<center>
<table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=300 style="margin: 30px 0px">
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{{currency group.balance currency=group.currency}}}</span></td>
    <td width=200>&nbsp;</td>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{group.backersCount}}</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="label">current balance</span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center" nowrap><span class="label">total backers</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.balanceDelta}}}{{{currency group.balanceDelta currency=group.currency}}})</span></span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.backersCountDelta}}}{{group.backersCountDelta}})</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br />
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#backers"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/backers.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#sponsors"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/sponsors.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
</center>

<h2>Expenses</h2>
<table width="100%" border=0>

{{#each group.expenses}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{{moment createdAt format="MM/DD"}}}</td>
    <td align="right">{{{currency netAmountInGroupCurrency currency=currency}}}</td>
    <td><a href="{{@root.config.host.app}}/groups/{{@root.group.id}}/expenses/{{id}}">{{description}}</a></td>
    <td class="{{toLowerCase status}}">{{toLowerCase status}}</td>
  </tr>
{{else}}
  No expense submitted. <a href="{{@root.group.publicUrl}}/expenses/new">Submit an expense</a>
{{/each}}
</table>

<h2>Newest sponsors on OpenCollective</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://opencollective.com/iDoneThis">iDoneThis</a>: they are committing $500/month to open source collectives</li>
<li><a href="https://opencollective.com/auth0">Auth0</a>: they are sponsoring open source projects related to authentication</li>
</ul>

{{#if group.related}}
  <h2>Newest related collectives</h2>
  <ul>
  {{#each group.related}}
    <li><a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">{{name}}</a>, on a mission to {{mission}} [<a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support that mission!</a>]</li>
  {{/each}}
  </ul>
{{/if}}

<h2>Featured collective</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://opencollective.com/FreeRideToVote?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">#FreeRideToVote</a>, on a mission to give a free ride to people who need one in order to go vote on November 8th. [<a href="https://opencollective.com/FreeRideToVote?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support that mission!</a>]</li> 
</ul>

<h2>Changelog</h2>
<ul>
<li>Check out our <a href="https://opencollective.com">new homepage</a> with featured collectives and sponsors</li>
<li>New Twitter and Meetup integrations; contact us if you want to test them!
  <ul>
    <li>Connect your Twitter account and automatically send a monthly thank you tweet mentioning your sponsors</li>
    <li>Connect your Meetup.com account and automatically add your backers and sponsors to your latest meetup description</li>
  </ul>
</li>
</ul>

</div>

{{> footer}}